ener noreferrer\">green operation<\/a> and saying no to plastic wherever possible!<\/p>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">It\u2019s no secret that <a href=\"https:\/\/www.glastonburyfestivals.co.uk\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Glastonbury Festival<\/a> champions the same principles and this year will be no different. As always\u00a0\u2013 it will be\u00a0Love and Peas, Love the farm and of course Leave no trace.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>We&#8217;re preparing to feed the UK&#8217;s most famous festival once again. Red Radish will be heading to Glastonbury Festival for another year of frolics and fantastic\u00a0artist and crew catering.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":13886,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[47,45,27,11],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-8956","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","hentry","category-artist-and-touring","category-crew","category-festivals","category-latest-blog-postings"],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v23.5 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>Catering for Glastonbury Festival 2019: Red Radish returns! - Red Radish<\/title>\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"We are looking forward to setting up our residency at Glastonbury for several weeks this summer to feed the fantastic\u00a0crew and artists.\" \/>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview:-1\" \/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/red-radish-returns-to-glastonbury-festival-2019\/\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"en_GB\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"article\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"Catering for Glastonbury Festival 2019: Red Radish returns! - Red Radish\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:description\" content=